OL,3,C'I've not joined for money or medals':
OL,4,Cpolice officer chases armed shoplifter
OL,6,FAn off-duty police response officer
OL,7,Fjumped into action and chased down a
OL,8,Fknife-carrying shoplifter in Arnold,
OL,9,FNottinghamshire.
OL,11,FPC Rishi Thobhani was off duty on
OL,12,FThursday 30 May and walking through
OL,13,Fthe High Street when he noticed
OL,14,FPoundland staff chasing after a man.
OL,16,FMichael Delaney, 32, was a prolific
OL,17,Fshoplifter known for intimidating
OL,18,Fstaff and using threats of violence,
OL,19,Fand had just stolen a number of items
OL,20,Ffrom the store.
