OL,3,C'I've not joined for money or medals':
OL,4,Cpolice officer chases armed shoplifter
OL,6,FPC Thobhani identified himself as a
OL,7,Fpolice officer and instructed him to
OL,8,Fstop. When Delaney refused, a chase
OL,9,Fbegan and in the course of that,
OL,10,FDelaney produced a large kitchen knife.
OL,12,FHe said: "As I've got closer, I've
OL,13,Fseen a knife, and then instantly
OL,14,Fbacked off.
OL,16,F"I've continued to shout 'knife' so
OL,17,Fpeople around me knew what was going
OL,18,Fon. Asked him to drop the knife
OL,19,Fmultiple times, he was then
OL,20,Fthreatening to stab me if I came near
OL,21,Fhim.
