OL,3,C'I've not joined for money or medals':
OL,4,Cpolice officer chases armed shoplifter
OL,6,F"There was a child on my side of the
OL,7,Fstreet, I've shouted to the child
OL,8,F'stay on that side of the street, man
OL,9,Fwith a knife'.
OL,11,F"My first thought was I can't let him
OL,12,Fgo onto this high street with a knife,
OL,13,Fso I took the decision that I'm going
OL,14,Fto challenge him.
OL,16,F"I was scared but, more so, the knife
OL,17,Fhas to come out of his hand, there's
OL,18,Fmembers of the public here."
