OL,3,C'I've not joined for money or medals':
OL,4,Cpolice officer chases armed shoplifter
OL,6,FHe managed to pull the knife away and
OL,7,Fdetain him, before further officers
OL,8,Farrived on the scene to take him into
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FPC Thobhani said: "My role at that
OL,12,Fmoment was to make sure no harm comes
OL,13,Fto anyone. I didn't think twice about
OL,14,Fwhat harm I would come to.
OL,16,F"I trusted my instincts and skills to
OL,17,Fapprehend Delaney.
