OL,3,C'I've not joined for money or medals':
OL,4,Cpolice officer chases armed shoplifter
OL,6,F"I've not joined the job for money or
OL,7,Fmedals. I know why I'm in the police
OL,8,Fand it is exactly why I did what I did
OL,9,Fon the day.
OL,11,F"Even if I wasn't a police officer,
OL,12,FI'd have done the same thing. I joined
OL,13,Fthe police to protect the community."
OL,15,FDelaney, aged 35, of no fixed address,
OL,16,Fwas arrested and charged. He pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty to a number of shop thefts,
OL,18,Fpossession of a bladed article and
OL,19,Fthreatening a person with a bladed
OL,20,Farticle.
